# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# stack-ops .gitignore — this repo is intended to become PUBLIC.
# The private/ layer + secret patterns below must NEVER be tracked.
# NOTE: .gitignore is a floor, not the gate. Before ANY push, a
# secret scan (gitleaks/trufflehog or a key-pattern grep over the
# full tree AND git history) + Mitchell's file-list review is
# MANDATORY. See private/HANDOVER.md § public-repo publishing gate.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Private layer: personal, confidential, pointers — never publish ──
private/
NOTES.md
*.private.md
*.local.md

# ── Secrets & credentials (defense in depth; values must never exist here) ──
.env
.env.*
*.env
.secrets
.secrets/
api-keys*
*credentials*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
service-account*.json

# ── Tooling / OS cruft ──
.DS_Store
node_modules/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.log
.vscode/
.idea/
